\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Congratulations! Meditation (Class) (Tier 2) has evolved to Meditation (Class) (Tier 3)! +1 Willpower point<!$Scr_Ps::0><$Scr_Ps::1>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f1\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 As he read carefully through the titles and skill evolutions, he found himself somewhat boggled by it all. What he\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d done had seemed so obvious given his Class imparted understanding of Magical Theory and his Mana Sensitivity Racial ability. Yet actually accomplishing it had dropped a slew of rewards on him, including removing his need for food and water. Now his body only needed his mana to fuel itself. Marcus had the System bring up just his stats so that he could see the progress.<!$Scr_Ps::1>}
