\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 His mana pool had more than doubled}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0  }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 between increases to his Core Compression and his Wisdom, putting him in a much stronger position as a Magus. At least he was much less likely to run short of Mana in a fight. He could only hope that his improved meditation skill was up to the task of keeping his Mana pool topped up without as much need for extended downtime. After all, he\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d just spent six full hours sitting here meditating and making other progress and now the Sun was sinking below the horizon.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus took stock of how he felt otherwise. As expected he was neither hungry nor thirsty, but he also felt no particular need to sleep as his meditation had also fully restored his Stamina and Soul Strength, clearing away both his physical and mental fatigue from the days activity. He considered continuing to move through the woods instead of making a camp of sort, but decided against it. Night was likely to bring out a variety of dangerous creatures who nod be even slightly disadvantaged by the lack of light. Without a better idea of what was out there to threaten him, it was a fool\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s errand. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Instead, he settled in to observe the nighttime forest for a while and see what he could learn. }
